Author.Name:
Becker, Carl (1867-?), German pharmacist (Rheinprovinz), born and educated in Viersen;

studied at the University of München 1890-1892, pharmaceutical state-examination 1892,

studied further at Strassburg and Erlangen, student of Max Rees at Erlangen. (C. Becker).

